import React from 'react'
import { FaEnvelope, FaReact, FaLinkedin, FaMedium, FaCalendar, FaGithub, FaDribbble } from 'react-icons/fa6'


export default function Icon({icon, size }) {
    let IconComponent;
    
    switch(icon) {
        case 'Email':
            IconComponent = FaEnvelope
            break
        case 'LinkedIn':
            IconComponent = FaLinkedin
            break
        case 'Medium':
            IconComponent = FaMedium
            break
        case 'Calendly':
            IconComponent = FaCalendar
            break
        case 'Github':
            IconComponent = FaGithub
            break
        case 'Dribbble':
            IconComponent = FaDribbble
            break
        default:
            IconComponent = FaReact
    }
    return <IconComponent size={size} />
}
